#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.mode.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.mode"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.mode.mode_dataframe:1 of
msgid "Get the mode(s) of each element along the selected axis."
msgstr "获取沿选定轴的每个元素的众数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.mode.mode_dataframe:3 of
msgid ""
"The mode of a set of values is the value that appears most often. It can "
"be multiple values."
msgstr "一组值的众数是出现频率最高的值。可能有多个值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.mode.mode_dataframe of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.mode.mode_dataframe:6 of
msgid ""
"The axis to iterate over while searching for the mode:  * 0 or 'index' : "
"get mode of each column * 1 or 'columns' : get mode of each row."
msgstr ""
"搜索众数时要迭代的轴：* 0 或 'index'：获取每列的众数 * 1 或 'columns'："
"获取每行的众数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.mode.mode_dataframe:6 of
msgid "The axis to iterate over while searching for the mode:"
msgstr "在搜索众数时遍历的轴："

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.mode.mode_dataframe:8 of
msgid "0 or 'index' : get mode of each column"
msgstr "0 或 'index'：获取每列的众数"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.mode.mode_dataframe:9 of
msgid "1 or 'columns' : get mode of each row."
msgstr "1 或 'columns'：获取每行的众数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.mode.mode_dataframe:11 of
msgid "If True, only apply to numeric columns."
msgstr "如果为 True，则仅应用于数值列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.mode.mode_dataframe:13 of
msgid "Don't consider counts of NaN/NaT."
msgstr "不考虑 NaN/NaT 的计数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.mode.mode_dataframe of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.mode.mode_dataframe:16 of
msgid "The modes of each column or row."
msgstr "每列或每行的众数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.mode.mode_dataframe of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.mode.mode_dataframe:21 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.mode`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.mode.mode_dataframe:22 of
msgid "Return the highest frequency value in a Series."
msgstr "返回 Series 中出现频率最高的值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.mode.mode_dataframe:24 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.value_counts`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.mode.mode_dataframe:25 of
msgid "Return the counts of values in a Series."
msgstr "返回 Series 中值的计数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.mode.mode_dataframe:28 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.mode.mode_dataframe:44 of
msgid ""
"By default, missing values are not considered, and the mode of wings are "
"both 0 and 2. Because the resulting DataFrame has two rows, the second "
"row of ``species`` and ``legs`` contains ``NaN``."
msgstr ""
"默认情况下，不考虑缺失值，翅膀的众数为 0 和 2。由于结果 DataFrame 有两行"
"，因此 ``species`` 和 ``legs`` 的第二行包含 ``NaN``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.mode.mode_dataframe:53 of
msgid ""
"Setting ``dropna=False`` ``NaN`` values are considered and they can be "
"the mode (like for wings)."
msgstr ""
"设置 ``dropna=False`` 时，会考虑 ``NaN`` 值并且它们可以成为众数（例如对于"
" wings）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.mode.mode_dataframe:60 of
msgid ""
"Setting ``numeric_only=True``, only the mode of numeric columns is "
"computed, and columns of other types are ignored."
msgstr "设置 ``numeric_only=True`` 时，仅计算数值列的众数，其他类型的列会被忽略。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.mode.mode_dataframe:68 of
msgid "To compute the mode over columns and not rows, use the axis parameter:"
msgstr "要按列而不是按行计算众数，请使用 axis 参数："

